		<div id='spacer'></div>
		<div id='example2' class=''>
			1 in 6 latrines in India are soon <br>abandoned after construction
		</div>
		
		<div id='spacer'></div>
		<img id='dirtydroplet' src=<%=asset_path "static/pngs/dirtydroplet.png"%>>
		<div id='unsafe' class="">
			Exposing people to unsafe water<br>
			sources and open
