			<span class='tinytext'>and the cycle of inequality within the WASH sector remains</span>
		</div>
		<div id='spacer'></div>
		<div id='spacer'></div>
		<div id='spacer'></div>
		<div id='lifecycle'>
		<div id="approach" class="">
			A life-cycle costs approach<br>
			<span class='tinytext'>shifts thinking</span>
		</div>
		</div>
		<div id='spacer'></div>
		<div id='spacer'></div>
		<div id='circles'>
			<div id="circle">
				<div id='circle2'></div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div id='circtext' class='tinytext'>from building isolated projects</div>
		<div id='line-container'>
			<div id='line'></div>
		</div>
		<div id='delivery-container'>
			<div id='delivery'>
				to delivering <br>
				long-term<br>
				services
			</div>
		</div>
		
		
		
		<div id='aspects'>
			ALL ASPECTS OF A SERVICE ARE <br>
			TAKEN INTO ACCOUNT
			<div class='tinytext'>from initial construction to ongoing maintenance<br>
				and eventual replacement.
			</div>
			<span class='tinytext'></span>
		</div>
		
		<div id='line2-container'>
			<div id='line2'></div>
		</div>
		<div id='calculator-container'>
			<div id='calculator'>
			<span>
				The WASHCost <br>
