			</div>			
			<div id="compare-text">
				Users can compare costs with  others<br>
				</div>
		<div id='clock-wrapper'>
			<div id='bobnclock'>
				<img id='rbauble' src=<%=asset_path "static/pngs/rbauble.png"%>><br>
				<img id='clock' src=<%=asset_path "static/pngs/clock.png"%>>
			</div>
			<div id='update-text'>
				The database is dynamically <br>
				updated as users enter data<br>
				<div>Growing smarter with each additional project</div>
			</div>
		</div>	
